*libmateweather-1.8.0 (11 Apr 2014)

  11 Apr 2014; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org> +libmateweather-1.8.0.ebuild:
  Version bump to 1.8.0.

  10 Mar 2014; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org> libmateweather-1.6.2.ebuild:
  Update dependencies per the consensus formed with ssuominen.

  10 Mar 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  libmateweather-1.6.2.ebuild:
  Remove guessed SLOT dependencies from gettext, intltool and pkg-config.

  10 Mar 2014; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org> libmateweather-1.6.2.ebuild:
  Further review of dependencies.

*libmateweather-1.6.2 (28 Feb 2014)

  28 Feb 2014; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org>
  +files/libmateweather-1.5.0-fix-automagic-python-support.patch,
  +files/libmateweather-1.6.1-fix-mkdirp.patch, +libmateweather-1.6.2.ebuild,
